time-in-service, whichever occurs first. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) For airplanes that have accumulated less than 6,000 total landings as of the effective date of this AD: Perform
the initial inspection at the later of the times specified in paragraphs (a)(1)(i) and (a)(1)(ii) of this AD. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(i) Prior to the accumulation of 6,000 total landings on the strut. Or 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(ii) Within 8 months after the effective date of this AD. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
