effective date of this AD: Perform the initial inspection within 6 months after the effective date of this AD. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(3) For airplanes that have accumulated 15,000 or more total landings as of the effective date of this AD: Perform the
initial inspection within 4 months after the effective date of this AD.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
