Entities claiming an exemption would be required to file this information on or before the payment due date for the
relevant regulatory fee category. If a showing is not properly documented or a claimed exemption is otherwise rejected,
an entity failing to pay the proper fee on time may be subject to a 25 percent late-payment penalty.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

