44. Mobile services. Licensed personal communications services (``PCS'') will consist of a wide variety of commercial
or private mobile communications services, including advanced paging, microcellular telephone communications,
portable facsimile and other video and data transmission services. See generally, First Report and Order, Gen. Docket
No. 90&hyph;314 and ET Docket No. 92&hyph;100, 8 FCC Rcd 7162, 58 FR 42681 (August 11, 1993) 
