against the United States for death; personal injury; or damage, loss, or destruction of property caused by military
personnel or civilian employees of the DA acting within the scope of their employment and incident to the noncombat
activities of the DA, provided such claim is not for personal injury or death of a member of the Armed Forces or Coast
