<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
All claims cognizable under subparts C, D and F which are based on damage to or loss of property due to explosions (for
example, artillery firing, aerial bombing, or demolition of explosives) will be sent through USARCS to U.S. Army
Ballistic Research Laboratories (USABRL), Aberdeen Proving Grounds, MD 21005&hyph;5055, for a technical opinion
