(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Tort Claims Memorandum. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Unless otherwise agreed between the USARCS AAO and the area claims office (see section 536.21(b)(1)), the contents
and arrangement of the Tort Claims memorandum will be as follows: 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Part I. Identifying Data. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

