<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
authority, the claim will be discussed with such authority prior to the furnishing of such advice. The claimant should
be 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
familiarized with all aspects of administrative settlement 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
procedures including the administrative channels through which the claim must be processed for approval. He or she
