<!-- PJG ITAG l=80 g=1 f=1 -->
&sect;536.88 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=89 g=1 f=1 -->
Procedures. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
So far as not inconsistent with this part, the procedures for the investigation and processing of claims contained
