<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Noncombat activities. 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
A claim incident to the noncombat activities of the ARNG while engaged in duty or training under 32 U.S.C. 316, 502,
503, 504, 505, or 709 may be settled under this subpart.
