(5) Unearned freight charges are deducted for property which carriers lose or irreparably damage. (See DA Pam 27&hyph;162,
paragraph 3&hyph;27.) 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(6) A claims office representative will periodically attend local transportation office outbound briefings to
ensure that appropriate information is being disseminated to soldiers. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(7) Inspections by claims office personnel are conducted in appropriate cases (large claim, reconsideration, fraudulent
claim) and incorporated into the file. 
