<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
As proposed, both Rule 10b&hyph;10 and Rule 15c2&hyph;13 will require broker-dealers to disclose when a debt security,
other than securities defined under Section 3(a)(42)(A) and (B) of the Exchange Act,
