with the National Environmental Policy Act (NEPA). See 516 DM [Departmental Manual] 2, appendix 1 Paragraph 1.10.
The proposed regulations are procedural in nature, and the environmental effects while crafted to carry out the benign
purposes of the WBCA, are judged to be minimal, speculative, and do not lend themselves to meaningful analysis. Future
regulations implementing the WBCA may be subject to NEPA documentation requirements, on a case-by-case basis. 
