endangered, threatened, vulnerable, not threatened, non-threatened or insufficiently known). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Sustainable use 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
